Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:06.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I had no idea there were so many \Ndifferent stalls for New Year's!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:11.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I've only ever been to smaller shrines, \Nso I've never seen anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Shinozaki-san, look! \NThey've got a shooting game!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.81,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! I was... not thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,No, please, don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm making such a fuss, \Nmy kohai is going to think I'm childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:35.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's making such a fuss... \NSenpai's acting like a kid.
