Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:41.94,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Do you think she's lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.23,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.07,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:48.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Where are your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:51.58,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,You were very brave \Nto hang in there on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:00.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you now, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:10.38,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Looks like she is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,That was really mature of you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Well, of course! I'm an adult, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:21.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,They've got a station for lost kids \Nat the reception desk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:22.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.21,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Look there, Yutaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:27.03,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:30.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,They look like parents \Nwith their child, don't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:35.76,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I can see it... my cute little sister, \Nand her cute little daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:38.21,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Would you two stop fussing? It's childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:46.10,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Oh, I love you so much, I just have to laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:55.72,Show_Title,Title sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H292A2F&\bord0}My {\1a&HFF&\bord1\3c&HA183CA&}T{\3c&H000000&}iny {\bord0\1a&H00&}Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:58.80,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,We've got an emergency here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.58,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Are you paying attention, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:07.81,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,There's someone other than me \Ndancing around inside of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.06,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I want to talk to her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.11,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I want to touch her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:18.60,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Look, I get it, but for now try to pipe down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.82,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,What in the world am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.58,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,You're right next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:30.83,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And this is the perfect chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:32.41,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,HONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:37.12,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I'm trapped by that sweet rich taste
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:40.33,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And I don't think I can ever escape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.83,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I may as well just sink into it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:43.66,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,HONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:48.43,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,It's another day in your dazzling presence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.43,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,We may never be \Non the same page with this love but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:57.87,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Oh, I love you so much, I just have to laugh
