Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.64,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}Time to start a new year of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:13.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:18.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to be \Nworking with you again, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:25.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hearing you call me that makes me \Nfeel like it's time to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you like it, I can call you that \Nwhenever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I have to say, New Year's went \Nby in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:35.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Considering you were a student last year, \Nit probably seems even faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:44.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}the angle at which I'm looking up at \NShinozaki-san is different from usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.49,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an5\shad0\fnComic Sans MS\c&H000000&\bord3\b1\3c&HFFFEFF&\fs20\pos(520,200)}Usual
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.49,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(475,0)\an5\shad0\fnComic Sans MS\c&H000000&\bord3\b1\3c&HFFFEFF&\fs20\pos(520,278)}Today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:54.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I would see him before, \Nmy head was around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I'm a little higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.86,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I gotten taller?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Shinozaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:07.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:14.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm a little different \Nthan usual today. Can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her clothes and shoes are different,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:25.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I don't think she'd ask \Nif it was something that obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:31.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Standard practice is to check nails, \Nbut those don't seem different...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,You can't tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.15,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,This scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.27,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.63,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Did you switch to a different shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I did, but that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:52.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got it wrong! A pervert! \NShe'll think I'm a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:57.13,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Shinozaki-san... \Nyou've been smelling my shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not like that, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swear, it wasn't anything untoward...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:06.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll need to be careful with my \Nshampoo choices going forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}He seems really stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:13.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should give him an obvious hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Okay, here's a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:21.89,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,It's not my hair or anything in particular \Nlike that, but more my body as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:24.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Your whole body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her whole... body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just told my kohai \Nto pay attention to my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:39.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,That's what you're into, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:42.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}A pervert! He'll think I'm a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.28,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,H-How about another hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:50.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,L-Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:54.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Well, there's a big size difference between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,That should make it pretty clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}A size difference... Th-Then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mean to say they've gotten even bigger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Well... I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Okay, here's the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,It turns out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:24.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Ta-da! I'm a little bit taller!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:29.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \Nyou do seem a bit taller...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}The boots... That explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:37.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're wearing \Nboots for a change, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:42.96,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\an8\fnComic Sans MS\b1\bord0\shad0\c&H312F36&\pos(429.334,19.333)}My boots...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:42.03,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,My boots... the soles...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\an8\fnComic Sans MS\b1\bord0\shad0\c&H312F36&\pos(163.333,49.333)}the soles...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna sit here \Nfor the rest of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.98,Main,Shionozaki,0,0,0,,But maybe you did get a bit taller!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.51,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,You don't need to humor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Well... Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:57.47,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I thought I was getting taller... Sulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:06:59.98,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Shinozaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:05.98,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,I've got something I'd like you \Nto take care of today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.98,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HF2F7F6&\bord0\shad0\blur2\3c&H000000&\an5\pos(553,300)}m 0 0 l 140 0 l 140 75 l 0 75
