Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:12.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Well, Katase-san oversees my scheduling, \Nso you'll need to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.99,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Don't be like that, Shinozaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.69,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,They do say, "when you're young,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.75,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,you should tackle \Nas many challenges as you can!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:21.76,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Pwease?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Making a cute face doesn't change the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:30.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,we're not in the habit of accepting challenges \Nthat don't actually serve a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.45,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Katase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.51,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:36.03,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,I-I thought you were in a meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:40.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Oh, so you asked Shinozaki-san about this \Nbecause you thought I wasn't around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.20,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Catch you next time, Shinozaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.45,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Ishiyama-kun never changes, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,An internal email?
