Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.53,Sign_Basic,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{\c&H4E5147&\3c&HF5FAF2&\shad0\fs24\an4\pos(196.667,282)}Wanna do it in secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Wanna do it in secret?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,He doesn't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.80,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hiss! Hiss! Hiss! Hiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Please stop trying to assign work \Ndirectly to my subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.40,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,But you wouldn't do it, Katase-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I never said I wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,But if you need something done,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:13.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,you need to talk to me first, \Nso we can do things properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.68,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,You mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.43,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,In that case, I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:23.33,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Katase-san really is quite the reliable senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.79,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.68,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}This should be doable \Nif we adjust the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.02,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really?! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,How'd your fortune turn out, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Tiny Senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.73,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still not used to being \N here at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:55.51,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:01.01,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}My boss can seem to appear out of thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:05.03,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,D-Don't scare me like that! \NI thought you were a ghost or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.41,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.63,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,But why are you working late \Nby yourself if you're scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.90,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Were you really that busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.40,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.31,Flashback,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Pwease?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:20.89,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ishiyama-san in PR said \Nhe needed this tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.49,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Did he get approval from \Nyour supervisor for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:27.30,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.13,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:32.13,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,He asked me right at the end of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.84,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,and said there was no one else \Nhe could turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.85,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Even so, fundamentally speaking, you really \Nshouldn't accept assignments on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.33,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Especially since you're new. Ask first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.14,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:46.45,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,But I thought, if I could just \Nget it done in secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.41,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Still no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:51.77,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,That'd just mean he's taking advantage \Nof how nice you are, Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:01.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,And speaking as a manager, \Nit's not nice at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.29,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,You're completely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:06.29,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,I'll have a word with Ishiyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.29,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Sorry about all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.69,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Well, it's part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:11.83,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.61,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.14,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,What?! What's wrong?! You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.57,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:28.47,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It's just, having someone looking out \Nfor me... made me so glad, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.63,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It's a real relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.13,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.45,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.82,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Have you eaten anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.33,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It was a rush job, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,How much longer do you think it'll be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.85,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I just need to submit it and I'll be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.09,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,If you've got time, \Ndo you wanna grab something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.09,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:01.82,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Consider it a little reward \Nfor a hard worker who made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.47,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can he just say stuff like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.52,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,The entrance made it look like \Nmodern residence,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.01,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,but it's got an old fashioned Japanese style.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.11,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Kinda surprising, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.24,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Tempting to just space out, taking it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.99,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! Why did he just sit next to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.48,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this a move?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.71,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he pulling some kind of move on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.00,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\c&H010301&\3c&HFAFBF8&\shad2\fs20\pos(218,185)}*Not really\Nthinking about it
