Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.00,Sign_Basic,Sign; top 3 headings,0,0,0,,{\fad(375,0)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\shad0\c&H586364&\3c&HE2F0F0&\an9\fs18\frx36\fry348\frz6.203\fax-.3\pos(568.667,70)}Drink Menu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.00,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What a big non-alcoholic selection!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.33,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I had no idea there was somewhere \Nlike this so close to the office.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:41.76,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,I noticed you almost never drink \Nwhen we have drinking parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.26,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,so I thought you might enjoy it a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:47.42,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you trying to be the ideal guy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.45,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What percentage of the office \Nhas confessed to you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:53.33,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}that{\i0} many!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't deny that he's been approached, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:02.13,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Manager... you never really talk about \Nyour romantic history, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.18,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,No one really asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:08.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,If I asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.65,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,If I asked, would you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.35,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,You wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.90,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I don't mean anything untoward by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Untoward how?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:25.93,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this just him? Is he just a ditz...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.95,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Romance, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:34.62,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,When I was younger, I didn't really \Nunderstand how it felt to like someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:37.71,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,I tried dating quite a few times \Nup through college,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.97,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,but in the end, I never really found love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:46.59,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,I think my life might just be one \Nwith no romance to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.86,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.09,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.08,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:59.09,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,Nothing makes me happier than \Ncheering on someone else's love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.62,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,I'm more curious about your \Nromantic history, Hayakawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.65,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,M-Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.25,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Now that reaction makes me curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.05,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Oho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.45,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I thought I recognized that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.60,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Yutaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:17.16,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Is your office around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:20.86,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Indeed. In the opposite direction of \Nthe station, though, so it's a bit of a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:25.36,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Some coworkers dragged me this way, \Nbut I've never been one for big groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.37,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,So I slipped out, but then realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.88,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,It's lonely to be on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:31.87,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\i1}So free-spirited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.28,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,That being the case, \Nwould you mind if I joined you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.21,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.81,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.00,Main - Top,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gimme pics of Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.37,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, what am I getting so anxious about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.97,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ask to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.45,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}Besides, I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.89,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}All she did was sit \Nin an empty seat, normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.00,Main - Top,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:48.89,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.66,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.51,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Chika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.02,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I think I'll sit here instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.28,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Just sit across the table \Nlike a normal person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.02,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.49,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I could see a wish for me to \Nsit here in those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.86,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Whose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:05.96,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:06.96,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Well, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:07.82,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.91,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,I guess... she didn't want to sit next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.29,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll sit here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.33,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,O-Onee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.71,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll just sit over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.09,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,You should sit here, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.96,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,No, no, that's for you, Yutaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.97,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.09,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.60,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Chika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.60,Main,Both,0,0,0,,If I'm interrupting, \NI'll head on home, so let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.45,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,Both of you sit down over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.19,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.81,Main,Hyakawa,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.61,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,You're really pouring it back, Chika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.01,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Are you a big drinker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.14,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,This is nonalcoholic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.92,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I see. Yet, you're still red.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.22,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body feels heavy for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this sleep paralysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:05.09,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Li'l Bro. Gimme some Shiorin-senpai pics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:11.59,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,It's just you?! And could you not barge \Ninto your brother's place on his day off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,And... pictures of Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.47,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Correct. Shiorin's fluffiness \Nwon't leave my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.24,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I want to have a picture on hand \Nso I can air-fluff her at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,What kind of reason is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:25.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,And what are those hand movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.11,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Air-fluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.11,Flashback,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Yes, quite fluffy indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:30.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:34.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don't have any pics \Nof Senpai in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.80,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Then get some.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,You should ask Hayakawa instead.
