Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:43.25,Main,Stamp signs,0,0,0,,{\an8\b1\fs20\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\fnComic Sans MS\pos(231.333,236.667)}No way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.50,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Your manager said to task you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Since when are you and my boss buddies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.01,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,We could... show each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:52.76,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,We could send each other \Npictures of us wearing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:58.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}We never did end up sending pics \Nof us wearing that loungewear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I can't deny I'd like to see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.37,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Yoink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.55,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,What did you just send?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Something from Shinozaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I miss you on the weekend..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:20.20,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Could you please send a picture \Nso I can see you whenever I want?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-Wh-Where did this\Ncome from all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:26.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-A-A-Am I dreaming?! \NAm I still asleep right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should bathe first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,My phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.35,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Okay, I've got it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Great, it's already marked as read!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.18,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(298.667,161.333)\bord0\shad0\c&H4E3F1A&\frz19.79}Read
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.52,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:45.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Senpai, it's a trick! \NThat was my sister! I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.94,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\an7\fs20\c&H5B5D51&\3c&HF4F7F4&\shad0\frz347.5\frx8\fry352\pos(236,200)}I'm so sorry!\NMy sister sent that!\NYou can ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:53.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,His sister? That explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,She replied!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:06.37,Sign_Basic,phone,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs16\c&H5B5D51&\3c&HF4F7F4&\shad0\frx8\fry352\pos(275.333,251.333)\frz17.17}...You sure\Nyou don't want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}You sure you don't want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.92,Sign_Basic,phone,0,0,0,,{\pos(134.667,283.333)\fs8\bord0\shad0\c&HFDFFFD&\frz16.06}Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.33,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Ask for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.17,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Could the peanut gallery pipe down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.34,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\c&H5B5D51&\3c&HF4F7F4&\shad0\frx8\fry352\frz331.8\pos(262,19.333)}I'm so sorry!\NMy sister sent that!\NYou can ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.34,Sign_Basic,Message Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\c&H394932&\3c&HA7F9CE&\shad0\frx8\fry352\pos(296.667,202)\frz331.1}...You sure\Nyou don't want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I actually sent that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:20.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now if he says he wants a picture, \NI should probably send one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sending a picture to Shinozaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? All of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:39.20,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm feeling really embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:42.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sending someone else a selfie like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:46.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who even does that \Nunless you're going out already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{also sign}"Senpai, I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.55,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,He's gonna say he wants one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,"I'm busy, so I'll be back later!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:02.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm partly relieved and partly frustrated! \NWhy am I so conflicted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:08.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,You had better apologize \Nto Senpai for bothering her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.65,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Consider it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.28,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,From Shinozaki-san's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:19.28,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiorin... Sorry about earlier. \NAllow me to make amends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.28,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sleeping brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.86,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother drinking bubble tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.62,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother with a kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.09,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother, running.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.69,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother, with sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:35.41,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}My brother, stretching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:37.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sh-She keeps sending pictures \Nof Shinozaki-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.25,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}My brother, writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.22,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother, in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.47,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait... in the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:46.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-W-Wouldn't that mean \NShinozaki-san is... n-na...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.35,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Age 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:02.74,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I never did hear back from Senpai yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Shinozaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.12,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Good morning, Shinozaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,G-G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:13.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Um... I'm sorry about \Nhow my sister acted yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,It's quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,And... about that picture you mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:23.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,If it's not too much trouble, \NI'd be really glad to receive one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:29.67,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said it! I actually said it! \NThere's no turning back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.81,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,When I stop and think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,there's something embarrassing \Nabout taking a picture of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:45.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all this, am I stuck on the \N"I changed my mind" path?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:46.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.03,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,why don't we take one together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,You and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:59.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,That way, it won't be a picture of just me, \Nbut a picture with you in it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:01.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.25,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Manager?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,How long have you been there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.89,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:10.31,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Shinozaki-kun, \Nget a little closer to Katase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.94,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I-Is there a reason I need to get closer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.44,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,There sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Are you nervous, Shinozaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:21.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.82,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:29.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm kind of nervous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:33.99,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.22,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:39.77,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Great! It turned out nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:46.19,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I was actually in a pair shot with Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:50.48,Main,Haykaawa,0,0,0,,Huh? What're you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.72,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:55.01,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Since you're here, \Nyou should take one with us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:55.73,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,You get in here, too, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.19,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.94,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Does a five second timer sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:02.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:03.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:06.70,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,Wait, what are we doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Hayakawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.95,Sign_Basic,Building sign,0,0,0,,{\move(136,320,100,320)\c&HC8C8C3&\bord0\fnArial\fs17\xshad-2\yshad2\fay-.05\frx0\fry358}D-Smart Pharmaceuticals
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.25,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(211.333,176.667)\fs12\bord0\shad0\b1\frz20.62}Lil Bro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.25,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H161B18&\3c&HF7FAF8&\shad0\fs18\an7\frz20.9\b1\pos(312,275.334)\fax.1}Sending pictures of\NSenpai etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:15.25,Italics,Yutaka,0,0,0,,A picture of Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.75,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, Li'l Bro, you finally have \Na picture of Shiorin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.25,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.51,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this "etc." mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:33.02,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I-I want in on this! I feel left out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:50.23,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:55.13,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:59.61,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:03.83,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And let it slowly spread throughout
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:08.79,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:13.68,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Where I once had some toast that glittered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:18.18,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,What is it that makes it so satisfying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:22.35,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Almost like magic
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:27.43,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I find myself thinking about that kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:33.03,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,How the small things can be the most precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.83,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Deep inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:42.23,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,It's ever so bittersweet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:47.15,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,"Just being around you is enough"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:51.17,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Becomes my mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:53.46,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Baby like sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:02.79,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Baby you're the sugar

